WEBVTT

00:00:01.122 --> 00:00:04.959
My life completely changed with one tweet.

00:00:05.960 --> 00:00:07.628
This was back in 2015

00:00:07.670 --> 00:00:12.467
when Twitter was mostly a place
we went to see what Kanye was mad about.

00:00:13.051 --> 00:00:15.219
But then I saw it.

00:00:16.304 --> 00:00:19.974
A tweet by a scientist I deeply admire,

00:00:20.016 --> 00:00:21.684
Dr. Carolyn Porco.

00:00:22.560 --> 00:00:26.397
Wait, I thought nuclear energy was bad.

00:00:26.773 --> 00:00:30.318
Yet here is a scientist
and a TED speaker